data.title: Te Dire Oui. V.H. Eau de Parfum 90ml
data.meta_description: D'Orsay Te Dire Oui. V.H. Eau de Parfum is a perfume that is an embodiment of unconditional love. A fragrance that speaks of love without limits. This scent captures the essence of love that knows no bounds, a profound connection that lingers in the heart.
data.text:
D'Orsay is a renowned perfume brand, celebrated for crafting elegant and timeless scents, intertwining traditional perfumery with innovative olfactive experiences, and embodying the sophistication and romance of Parisian charm.

——————————————————————

The embodiment of unconditional love. Saffron, Black Pepper, Pink Berries, and Incense create a captivating symphony. In the heart, Nagarmotha, Leather, Rose, and Sandalwood unite, like an unwavering bond.

The base notes of Styrax, Benjoin, Mousse, and Musk leave an enduring imprint, a fragrance that speaks of love without limits. This scent captures the essence of love that knows no bounds, a profound connection that lingers in the heart.

——————————————————————

Each bottle comes with a complimentary matching sample to allow for testing the fragrance on your skin. Suitable for any gender.

We recommend storing your perfume in a dark and cool place like a cabinet or in the refrigerator.

——————————————————————

Top Notes

Saffron — Black Pepper — Pink Berries — Incense

Heart Notes

Nagarmotha — Leather — Rose — Sandalwood

Base Notes

Styrax — Benjoin — Mousse — Musk

——————————————————————

Master Perfumer

Vincent Ricord

——————————————————————

Made in France.

All orders are prepared with care and finished with a Mr Floral gift note. Complementary shipping is available for all orders over £100.

Expected delivery time is 1-2 business days (Mon-Fri). All orders are dispatched via Royal Mail Tracked 24. You will receive an e-mail confirmation with your tracking number once your order is dispatched.

If you have any queries regarding your order, please e-mail us on orders@mrfloral.co.uk.
